ports.behavior:
forward patient_list
assign LevelBeforeEncryption.High if Level.High
assign LevelBeforeEncryption.Low if Level.Low
set Level.Low
unset Level.High

forward patient_list_encrypted,request
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from patient_list_encrypted,request
assign Level.High if Level.High from patient_list_encrypted,request

forward patient_list_encrypted,request
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from patient_list_encrypted,request
assign Level.High if Level.High from patient_list_encrypted,request

forward permissions
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from permissions
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from app_code
assign Level.High if Level.High from permissions
assign Level.High if Level.High from app_code
